<br>
&quot;I'm not sure why you keep trying. It's rather disturbing to watch. It's almost as if you really believe you can change anyone's mind who posts here.&quot; <br>
<br>
I am really not trying.  I'm just responding back to the crap these idiots are posting.  If that in itself is reason to think ill of me that so be it.  Life is really too short to care what complete strangers actually think.<br>
